Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Beware stereotypes, 1984
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xdc9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Jun 1984
Latest national statistics prove that basing our assumptions on stereotypes will inevitably prove us wrong. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less